sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Pilot as Pilot Lab
    participant Sec as BIPM / KCDB Secretariat
    participant Part as Participant (NMI/DI)
    participant Subm as Submission Service
    participant Comp as Computation Service
    participant Rev as CC Reviewers / WG
    participant KCDB as KCDB System
    participant CMC as CMC Validation Service

    Pilot->>Sec: Draft protocol & request registration
    Sec->>KCDB: Register comparison (ID, metadata)
    Sec-->>Pilot: Provide comparisonId & schema
    Sec-->>Part: Publish protocol + submission schema

    Part->>Subm: Submit results + uncertainty package
    Subm->>Subm: Validate syntax & vocabularies

    alt Submission valid
        Subm-->>Part: Acknowledge acceptance
        Subm->>KCDB: Store submission (versioned)
    else Submission invalid
        Subm-->>Part: Return validation errors
        Part->>Subm: Correct & resubmit
        Subm->>Subm: Re-validate
        Subm->>KCDB: Store corrected submission
    end

    KCDB-->>Comp: Provide frozen dataset
    Comp->>Comp: Compute KCRV / CRV
    Comp->>Comp: Compute DoE & DoE uncertainty
    Comp->>KCDB: Store provisional results
    Comp-->>Rev: Provide dataset + computation report

    Rev->>Rev: Review results & methods
    alt Accepted
        Rev-->>Comp: Approval
    else Revision requested
        Rev-->>Comp: Issues & revision request
        Comp->>Comp: Recompute with adjustments
        Comp-->>Rev: Updated results
        Rev->>Rev: Re-review
    end

    Comp->>KCDB: Publish final results package
    Sec->>KCDB: Register as official KCDB record (version)

    KCDB-->>CMC: Provide DoE evidence
    CMC->>CMC: Link DoEs to CMC claims
    CMC->>CMC: Perform validation checks (En, rules)
    CMC->>KCDB: Store validation outcomes & evidence trail
